title: Arianespace to Launch Europe’s Final Mission of 2023 Aboard Vega in September
summary:
After ESA confirmed Ariane 6 would not debut until 2024 and the return to flight of Vega C suffered a setback following a failed test, it appears that Europe can look forward to just one more launch in 2023.
